name: Do, Or Do Not
Lore: 'A Jedi may choose to intervene in the natural course of events, but must accept responsibility for the consequences.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Sense and Alter are now Lost Interrupts. Also, when and player makes a destiny draw for Sense or Alter, and that destiny draw is successful, that player loses 2 Force. (Immune to Alter.)',
